text:
I wish I could be more of assistance here but I haven't deployed the suggested CSS myself.

I would dive into that community post and check out the few examples that are near the last few pages of comments, <https://community.HubSpot.com/t5/HubSpot-Ideas/More-Chat-Widget-Styling-Options/idc-p/302187/highlight/true#M45464|here >and for the chat container size on mobile <https://community.HubSpot.com/t5/HubSpot-Ideas/More-Chat-Widget-Styling-Options/idi-p/13806/highlight/true/page/4#comments|here>.

Below is the snippet provided from the first link above:
```&lt;style&gt;
#HubSpot-messages-iframe-container {
bottom: 80px !important;
max-height: calc(100% - 80px) !important;
}
.bottom-left-widget{
bottom: 100px;
}
&lt;/style&gt;```
